Class KBModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.complexible.common.openrdf.model.DelegatingModel

    public final class KBModel
extends DelegatingModel

    An implementation of a Graph which acts as a VERY minimal OWL knowledge base. In this case, it simply provides convenience functions for adding and removing OWL expressions directly.
